➜和牛汉堡，在朋友圈刷到26次，终于忍不住去了...
http://www.sohu.com/a/437273549_100131509	42675
<h1></h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201209/18f2d92613ab433dafac6fa222789a55.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201209/072a5d02bf504efebfad6c954875399e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>／在法律允许范围内，活动解释权归品牌所有／</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201209/b76e67b5fb034286b6fca156703052ba.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
